de.mcp.cutcad.model

Class ObjectContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mcp.cutcad.model.ObjectContainer

  • public class ObjectContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    The object container is a model object to collect and manage all geometric instances of the project. It keeps track about changes in the project and allows for saving, loading and clearing the current project.
    Author:
    dennis
